File Naming:
- Always prefix environment files with dot (.)
- Use descriptive names after the dot

Security:
- Never commit environment files to version control
- Add all .env* files to .gitignore
- Use .env.example for template files
- Keep sensitive data in .credentials files

Structure:
- One variable per line
- Use KEY=value format
- No spaces around equals sign
- Use UPPER_SNAKE_CASE for variable names
- Add comments with # prefix